_header: At Antioch as men han said / Dwelled some time a maid
Title(s): South English Legendary ; De quadam virgine in anthiocha
_description: De quadam virgine in anthiocha, in one MS of the South English Legendary — in couplets

BodEngPoeta1.First Lines:
At Antioche as men han saydeDwellede sum tyme a
                    Mayde…
BodEngPoeta1.Last Lines:
…But as God wolde for þe nonesÞei toke heor Coroune
                    boþe at ones
